  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This standard is an extension for [ERC-721](./eip-721.md), designed to specify users for various contexts with a locking feature and allow temporary ownership delegation without changing the original owner. This EIP preserves the benefits and rights of the owner while expanding the utility of NFTs across various dApps by adding the concepts of Ownership Delegation and Contexts, which define specific roles: Controller and User, who can use the NFT within defined contexts.",
  "title": "Ownership Delegation and Context for ERC-721"
}